Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:08.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がつけば 地の底の底
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.13,0:00:11.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji came to in an underground slave labor facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:12.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強制労働施設に\N放り込まれたカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:16.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His only hope for escape, a one-day furlough pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:16.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脱出する唯一の希望は１日外出券
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:20.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなカイジの前に立つ この男\N班長 大槻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:20.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And now his team leader, Ohtsuki, stands before him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:25.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだい 今夜あたり\Nこいつで復活ってえのは？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:25.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How about it? Why not get back to your old habits tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:32.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A devil beckons from the abyss! The dice game chinchirorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:32.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪魔が誘うサイコロ賭博\Nチンチロリン
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.35,0:00:40.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,500)\pos(640,505)}The Rules of the Game
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:49.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, you're supposed to be great at this, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:49.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君は すご腕なんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.26,0:00:52.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,噂じゃ ここの大幹部を倒したとか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:52.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I heard you took down the big shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:56.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１億円 張ったとかさ\N関係ねえって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:54.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,and that you toss a hundred million yen around like it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.91,0:00:59.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter. I lost in the end, and that's why I'm here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:59.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 負けて\Nこんな所にいるようじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.30,0:01:01.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大バカ野郎も いいとこだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:01.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm a damned fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:05.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if you're a fool, look who you're comparing yourself with.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.30,0:01:05.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 仮にバカだとしても\Nスケールが違う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.44,0:01:09.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここの連中ときたら\Nスケールの小さい奴ばかりでよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:09.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,These guys are all small fries.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:14.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You'll never get anywhere playing them for matchsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.81,0:01:13.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかく勝負しても\Nチマチマ張ってばかりで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:15.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全然 胸が高まらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:20.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm in charge here, so as long as everyone's having fun, that's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:18.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 班長としては\N皆が楽しんでくれれば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:20.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それはそれで いいんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:25.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本音を言えば\Nもっと熱い勝負がしたいわけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:25.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But to be honest, I really want to put more on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.13,0:01:28.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君みたいな男と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.29,0:01:27.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Up against someone like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.03,0:01:32.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや もちろんカイジ君とわしじゃ\N格が違うんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.05,0:01:36.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Honestly, you're way out of my league, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.37,0:01:36.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらとしては当然\N胸を借りるつもりなんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:39.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼むよ こいつでさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:39.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,C'mon! You can bet this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:48.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,６万借りても倍の12にすりゃ\Nいいだけの話じゃない な？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:47.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if you have to borrow sixty thou, everyone'll be happy if you turn it into one-twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.29,0:01:51.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ野郎\Nその倍が簡単にできりゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.41,0:01:51.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fool! Is that all you think I can do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:53.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃ こうしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:53.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:57.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普段は６万借りたら\N結果はどうあれ 返す時には
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:02:01.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you waited until payday, you'd have to pay me back ninety thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:02:01.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正規の給料分９万で返すのが\N決まりなんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.57,0:02:04.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回は特別 今夜中に返せば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:05.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But if you pay me back the sixty tonight, we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.17,0:02:07.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チャラってことにしよう\Nチャラ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:07.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:11.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If he doubles it to 120,000, he can easily pay back the advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.07,0:02:11.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,倍の12万に増やせば\N６万返して前借りは清算
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:15.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手元には６万が残り\N今月をしのげる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:15.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He'd be left with 60,000 for the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:19.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これさ これが今\Nカイジ君が体勢を立て直す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:21.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,See, this is the best way to set yourself up with a stack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.02,0:02:21.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ベストな方法じゃないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:27.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チッ　おだてたり すかしたり\Nこの班長 意外に食えねえな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:26.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Buttering me up and making a show of things... This guy's sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:31.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが確かに そうかも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:30.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But, he may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:35.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このまま400ぽっちを手に\N禁欲生活を送ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:35.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I starve myself by trying to live on four hundred in pocket change,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:38.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll blow it all again the next payday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:38.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また給料日には\N爆発しちまいそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:45.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And if I borrow that money and win tonight's game...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:46.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それより その金を借りて\N今日のｷﾞｬﾝﾌﾞﾙで少しでも勝てば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:51.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,むろん負けたら\N更に最悪な状況に追い込まれる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:50.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But if I lose, then I'm really fucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:55.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし相手は あの利根川や\N会長のような猛者とは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:56.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then again, they're nowhere near as serious as Tonegawa or the President...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:57.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほど遠い連中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:03:00.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな連中に俺が負けるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:59.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Is it even possible for me to lose against them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:03.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けるわけがねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:02.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:06.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今夜中に返せば６でいいんだな？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:06.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's sixty thousand if I pay you back tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:09.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,On my honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:09.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしも男だ　二言はない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:17.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開いてくれ\Nおお そうこなくっちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:13.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hand it over, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:15.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You didn't even need to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:20.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Gambling is officially banned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:19.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,基本的には賭博は御法度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:23.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが就労者の\Nガス抜きの意味もあり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:23.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But, in order to allow the workers to let off steam,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:26.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,各班の班長が\N責任を持つことを条件に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:27.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,the leaders of each team, if they accept responsibility for the consequences,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:30.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,月に２～３回の開帳が認められる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:30.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,are allowed two or three gaming nights a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:34.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大槻 今宵の賭博開帳の許可を得る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:34.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ohtsuki has received permission to hold a gambling night. {edit}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:36.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ようし 開帳だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:36.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:39.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, Isawa, Numakawa! Get everything ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:39.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 石和 沼川　準備しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:41.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい\Nお…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:40.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:46.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けねえ こんな連中に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not to these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:48.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けるはずがねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:48.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:52.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通常 ９時半には消灯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Normally, lights out is at 9:30 sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:55.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが場を開く部屋は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:59.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But in rooms where gambling is taking place, this is extended to 11:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:04:00.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特別に11時半まで\N消灯延長が許される
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:04.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,参加者は両替後\N参加費300ペリカを支払い
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:02.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The participants, after making change,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,buy into the game for 300 perica,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:07.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おのおの好きな席に着く
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,and then take their seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:12.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Twice a month, on the first and third Saturdays,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:11.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,月に２回 第１第３土曜に\N開かれる場では
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:15.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他の班からも大人数が参加する
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:14.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,members of other teams are allowed to participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:18.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But as tonight's games were called on short notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:20.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…が 今夜の集まりは\N急きょ 決まったもの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:22.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,集まりは小規模
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:22.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,few are in attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:26.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, we've got two new players tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:26.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さて今夜は初参加が２人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:29.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君と三好君だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:29.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji and Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:35.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人はチンチロの経験は？\N一応 何回か
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:33.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Have either of you ever played chinchiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:36.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:38.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は実は一度も…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:38.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just... Just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:41.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まったくの初心者で… すいません
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:42.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm pretty new at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:46.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいさ いいさ\Nそれじゃ簡単に説明しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:46.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No worries. Let me explain the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:51.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,To play chinchiro, you roll three dice in a bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:51.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チンチロってのは サイコロを３つ\Nどんぶりに投げ込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:53.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出た目で勝ち負けが決まる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:53.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Your roll decides whether you win or lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:56.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,サイコロを振るのは\N１人３回まで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:58.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Each person can roll the dice up to three times. Simple, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:58.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,簡単だろ？\Nはあ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:01.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一番最初に親が振る
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:01.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The dealer rolls first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:05.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それから左回りで順番に子が振る
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:05.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then the players, in clockwise order.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:10.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親と子 どちらの目が強いかで\N金が行き来する
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:10.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Whoever has the best roll between the dealer and the other players takes the pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:14.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So it's a game in which each player is up against the dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:14.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いわば親対子の勝負ってわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:18.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,で こいつが目の強い順番だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:17.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And here's how you tell which roll wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:21.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チンチロの出目とは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:26.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A chinchiro roll is the value of the third die after the other two come up a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:24.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３つのサイコロのうち\N２つの同じ目を出して
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初めて目として成立する
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:29.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２つの目が２　そして残りが１
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:29.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If two dice come up 2 and the last comes up 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:32.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この場合は出目が１
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:32.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The player has rolled a 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:34.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If this happens, they've rolled a 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:34.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この場合は６
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:38.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出目の順位は\N６が最も強く １が弱い目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:38.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of the rolls, 6 is thestrongest, 1 is the weakest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:44.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然 強い目を出した者が勝者\N張った分の金額を得る
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:41.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The man with the highest roll wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:43.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He takes the pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:47.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３つの目がバラバラの状態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:47.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If all the dice come up differently,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:50.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これを目なしと呼ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,it's a bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:53.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この場合 ３回まで\Nサイコロを振ることができるが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:53.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In this case, the player can roll up to three times,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:57.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３回振って目なしなら負けが確定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:57.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,but three busts in a row are an automatic loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:06:00.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,張った金を失うことになる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:05:59.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They then lose their bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:06.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただし この３つのﾊﾞﾗﾊﾞﾗの目にも\N２つ特例がある
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:05.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But there are two special rules on unmatched numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:10.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シゴロ\Nこの目が出た時は２倍づけ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,4, 5, and 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:09.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A player who rolls this wins double their bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.85,0:06:13.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Twice the money they'd wagered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:13.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すなわち張った金額の倍を得る
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:15.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, a 1, 2, and 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:17.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆にヒフミ\Nこの目が出た場合は倍払い
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:18.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A player who rolls this loses double their bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:21.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すなわち張った金額の\N２倍を払うことになる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:21.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Also twice the money they'd wagered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:28.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And the strongest roll...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:28.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして最も強い出目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:32.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それがこいつ　ゾロ目だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:31.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Three of a kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:35.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここじゃ\N２から６のゾロ目が３倍づけ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:35.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Triples of 2 through 6 win triple the bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,更に１の目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:36.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And then, triple 1s...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:40.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Snake eyes win five times the original wager.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:40.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このピンゾロは\N５倍づけってことになる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:42.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Five times!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ご… ５倍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:47.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハ そんなにビビらなくても\Nそうそう出る目じゃないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:46.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:48.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They don't come up that often.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:50.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１つ ションベンといって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:50.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And then there's the "pisser."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:54.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなふうにサイコロが\Nこぼれた場合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:57.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If a die rolls out of the bowl, we treat it as a bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:57.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うちでは目なしと決めている
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:07:02.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if the dealer rolls a bust, if the player rolls a pisser he loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:07:02.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たとえ親が目なしでも\N子がションベンすれば親の勝ちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:06.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そしてションベンを出した時点で\N次はサイコロを振れない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:06.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And if you roll a pisser, you're not allowed to reroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:10.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初にこぼしたら\Nあとの２回は振れないってわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:09.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Do it on your first try, and your other two are forfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:14.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さて ここからが肝心なんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:15.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And last, but not least...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:18.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うちのチンチロには\N３つの特殊ルールがある
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:18.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We have three special rules down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:20.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特殊ルール？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Special rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:23.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're nothing really special.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:25.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それほど大げさなもんじゃないが\Nルールの付け足しってところだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just a few tweaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:29.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特殊ルールその１\N親の総取りはなし
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:28.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Special rule number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The dealer can't win automatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:39.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Normally, when the dealer rolls a 6, a 4-5-6, or triples, they automatically win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:37.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通常 親が振って\N出目６やシゴロ ゾロ目を出せば
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:39.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その時点で親の勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:42.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They receive everyone's bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:42.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金は親の総取りとなる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:44.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし地下チンチロでは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:50.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But in underground chinchirorin, no matter the dealer's roll, the players can attempt to beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:47.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親がどんなに\Nそれら強い目を出しても
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:50.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,子はサイコロを振ることができる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:55.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If the dealer rolls a 6, the player can force a draw by doing the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:56.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮に親が出目６を出しても\N子が同じ６を出せば引き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:08:02.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シゴロやゾロ目を出せば\N逆に子の勝ちということになる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:08:00.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If he rolls 4-5-6 or triples, he could even win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:06.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな苦しい中 ギリギリの金で\N遊んでいるんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:06.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I know none of you have much money to spare,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:10.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親の総取りは あっけないし\Nあんまりだってことでな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:10.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,so it's just unfair for the dealer to take all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:16.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, even if the dealer rolls 1-2-3, it's a draw if the player rolls a pisser.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に親が\N倍払いのヒフミを出しても
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:18.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,子がションベンなら分け\N親の総払いもなしってわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:18.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The dealer doesn't have to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:24.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特殊ルールその２\N親はスルーできる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:23.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Special rule number two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:24.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The dealer can pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:26.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Can pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:26.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スルーできる？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:33.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Passing. If he feels like he doesn't have enough money or the dice aren't on his side,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:28.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スルー　すなわち
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:33.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金に余裕がなかったり 自分の目が\N下がっていると思ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:35.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親をパスすることができる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:35.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,the dealer can pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:42.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course, he's welcome to play as usual the next time it's his turn. {to deal? fff this game for not having cards}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:37.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もちろん１度パスしても
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:40.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次に順番が回った時\N受けるかどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:43.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それも自由だ　オッケーかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:43.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:48.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Special rule number three!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:48.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特殊ルールその３
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:51.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親を続けられるのは２回まで\N２回？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Turns as dealer last only two rounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:51.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Two rounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:55.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親のバカ勝ちを避けるため\N親は２回まで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:54.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,To keep the dealer from taking everyone to the cleaners,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:55.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,each player is only dealer twice in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:59.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次の隣の者に\N親が移るというシステム
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:58.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, the next player in the sequence is dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:05.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただし親が１発目に\N目なしや１の目を出したら即交代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:04.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But if the dealer rolls a bust or a 1 on his first turn, it changes immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:08.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１回交代もあり得る\Nああ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:07.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So it can change after a round, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:11.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, and there's a bet restriction of twenty thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:12.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それと賭けの上限は２万まで\N２万…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:12.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Twenty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:16.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ以上ドカドカ張られたら\N親が持たねえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:16.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't want to break the bank, now, would we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:20.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど\Nだが親が受けるというなら別
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:17.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:20.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is at the dealer's discretion, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:22.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,上限なしだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So it's not really a limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:27.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you want to risk it all, just wait until I'm dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:27.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大きく張りたくなったら\Nわしの親の時に来るがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:29.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll take that bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.41,0:09:29.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは受けてやるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:31.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No matter how high.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:32.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくらでも
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:36.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや チビチビいきますよ\Nしばらくは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:33.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:36.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll keep it low for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.52,0:09:42.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ　そりゃ当然\N最初からバカ張りはできんよな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:39.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:42.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You can't go all in at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:44.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:43.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Anyways...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:49.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そろそろ参ろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:49.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:59.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地下チンチロ 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:57.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Underground chinchiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:09:59.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:07.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ 張った 張った
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:05.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Place your bets!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:09.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In underground chinchiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:13.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地下チンチロ　通例として\N班長大槻の親から始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:12.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,the team leader, Ohtsuki, usually goes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:16.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ　張りは100ペリカ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:16.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji bets 100 perica.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:19.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初は様子見だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:18.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,First, I'm going to see how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Take it easy and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:21.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ユルユルいって待つ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:25.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強く張れる その機を
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:24.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait for the moment to strike...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:27.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大槻 １投目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:27.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ohtsuki's first roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:34.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出目は５\N初っ端から悪いな 皆の衆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:34.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Looks like you gentlemen are out of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:42.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何やってんだ\Nいや 出目をメモして…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:39.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:43.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, just writing down your roll...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:45.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,野暮なことするなよ\Nあ… はあ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:44.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Knock it off, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:50.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあまあ　いいじゃないか\N楽しみ方は人それぞれだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:47.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Cool it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:51.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. Everyone has their own way of having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:53.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや しかし…\N好きにしな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:52.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:56.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:56.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:10:58.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here, your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:58.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほれ　お前の番だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:02.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ　まあ班長さえよければ\N俺は別に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:02.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:06.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,続いて子の１番手 沼川
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:05.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Next, the first player, Numakawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:08.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He rolls 1-2-3 and pays double!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:08.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヒフミ　倍払い
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:12.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっちゃー！\Nツいてないのう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Aw shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:12.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's just not your day, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.68,0:11:15.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:24.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして来る
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:23.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And it arrives!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.13,0:11:28.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの初振り
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:26.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's first turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:30.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その１投目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:30.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And his first roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:43.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんと初っ端でシゴロ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:44.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Amazingly, it comes up 4-5-6 on his first roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:47.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすが カイジ君　参ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:47.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wow, you really are {\i1}the{\i0} Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:51.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも助かったよ 張りが100で
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:50.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Guess I'm lucky you bet so low.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:57.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ？シゴロは倍づけで200\N１枚余分じゃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:55.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm, 4-5-6 is double, so I get 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:57.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You gave me one too many.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:12:02.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかくのシゴロだってのに\N張りが100じゃかわいそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:12:01.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You deserve better than a bet of 100 for a leadoff 4-5-6 will earn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:05.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Take it. As a consolation prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:05.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１枚は残念賞　取っておきな\Nどうも
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:06.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:08.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なになに　さあ次は三好君だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:07.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:08.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Anyways, your turn, Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:10.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は… はい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:09.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:14.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハア　残念賞か　確かにそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:14.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Consolation prize, huh? I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:17.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかくの倍づけも\N張りが100じゃな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:16.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if it's double, it's still only {\i1}two{\i0} hundreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:23.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや まだ流れも見えない１投目だ\N仕方ない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:21.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But... I can't read the table yet. Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:27.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに この振りは\N勝負の肝じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:26.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Plus, this isn't the real meat of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:30.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このチンチロは親対子の勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:29.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Chinchirorin is a game played against the dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:32.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親で いかに勝つか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:32.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When you're the dealer, you can win it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:35.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それっ　あー！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:40.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に言えば親の時\Nいかに負けないか　そこが肝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:38.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But it's vital to not lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.18,0:12:40.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's the meat of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:45.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このチンチロを制するカギ\N急所だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:43.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's the key to winning at chinchirorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:48.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待つんだ 辛抱強く 流れを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:48.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait... Wait patiently for the flow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:54.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし一進一退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:54.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But as the game continues,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:57.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji cannot feel the flow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:13:00.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジには流れが感じられない\N意識がぼやけている
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:59.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He begins to lose focus...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:04.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然 張りが100では意識が希薄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:04.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Betting hundred by hundred is not enough to hold his attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:06.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,流れなど感じられるはずもない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:07.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for him to feel the flow like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:10.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この少額の張りでは\N勝った時に うれしさより
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:12.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,With these tiny sums, a win brings not joy, but disappointment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:15.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,むしろガッカリ 落胆\N惜しいという気持ちが大きい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:15.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His regret grows!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:19.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に負けると どこかホッとする
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:18.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even a loss would be a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:22.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通常のギャンブルの思考と逆\N言い換えれば
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:22.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's the opposite of normal gambling...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:27.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The sensations of a normal game are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:27.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャンブルにおける正常な感覚\N生理から離れてしまっている
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:34.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことで熱を 勢いを
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:34.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The passion... The spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:40.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるいは幸運の兆し 気配 兆候を
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:39.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The feel of Lady Luck's gaze, the atmosphere, the little signs...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:43.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,感じられるはずがないのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:43.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He can feel nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:52.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開始から40分\Nカイジ ようやく己の愚に気づく
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:52.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,40 minutes after the game begins, Kaiji realizes his folly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:56.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカか 俺は　賢明ぶりやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:56.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Am I a fool for trying to outsmart them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:14:00.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムダな張りをしねえとか\Nこれじゃダメなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:14:00.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm wasting my time with these tiny bets!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:03.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,小さく張った時は負けて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:06.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Lose small and win big, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:06.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大きく張った時に勝つ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:11.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいおい\Nそりゃ それが博打の理想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:11.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's the gambler's ideal, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:14.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが理想であって基本じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:14.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But it's the ideal, not how it actually works!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:19.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャンブルとは\Nもっと泥仕合 愚かなもの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:17.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Gambling is dirtier than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:19.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:23.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It doesn't work without a twinge of pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:23.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヒリつかなきゃダメなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:31.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３度勝てば顔は紅潮し\N体温は上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:30.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If he wins three times, his face glows and his temperature rises!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.61,0:14:36.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に３度負けたら血が逆流
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:35.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But if he loses three times, his blood freezes in his veins!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:39.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それがギャンブルの張りの基本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:39.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That is the truth of betting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:56.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな張りを続けてこそ\Nほの見える分岐点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:55.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His wagers bring him to the crossroads!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:00.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,流れが変わる時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.28,0:15:06.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When the flow changes, he can feel the waves of fortune lapping at his feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:06.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強運の波動 熱く張れる場所を\N感じられるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:12.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうやめだ ケチな勝負は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:11.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm done playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:15.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親 あんたの番だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:13.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:15.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:31.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スルーだ\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:29.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:34.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺には まだ流れが\Nまるで見えていない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:34.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I still can't really feel the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:37.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで親を受けるのは早い
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:36.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's too soon to play the dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:39.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何 固まってんだよ\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:39.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Who put the stick up your ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:44.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうせ お前も親はスルーだろ？\Nいや その…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:42.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What, you gonna pass, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:44.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:46.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで一度も受けてないしな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:47.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You haven't laid a single bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:50.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや でも\Nやってみようかな 今回は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:50.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:55.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうそう　ﾁﾝﾁﾛは親を受けてこそ\Nだいご味を味わえるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:55.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Playing dealer is the best part of chinchirorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:57.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やったほうがいいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:57.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:59.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:59.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それじゃやります
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:04.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ皆の衆　三好君の初親だ\N張った 張った
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:03.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay, gentlemen! It's Miyoshi's first turn as dealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:04.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Place your bets!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:14.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え… えー！3000ペリカ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:14.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,3,000 perica!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.02,0:16:16.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:20.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして　今までずっと\N100ペリカだったのにどうして
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:17.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:20.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You've been betting 100 all this time! Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:22.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ どうして？ねえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:22.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on, why? Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:24.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うるせえ！博打に\Nどうしてこうしてがあるか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:25.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shut up! There's no "why" in gambling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:28.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,張る時は張るんだよ\Nそんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:26.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You just lay your money down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:28.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:33.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあまあ三好君　なにも\N取られると決まったわけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:33.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There, there, Miyoshi. You haven't lost yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:36.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,案外 大儲けするかもしれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:36.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You might do better than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:39.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃそうだけど\Nさあ振って振って
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:38.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:39.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:43.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも何だかな…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:41.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:49.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よりによって１かよ\Nよし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:48.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Aww man, a 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:49.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:55.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In normal chinchiro, if the house rolls a 1, the players win automatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:52.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通常チンチロは\N親が１の目を出すと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:56.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,子は振ることなしに勝ち\N親の総払いとなるが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:56.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The dealer pays out to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:59.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この地下チンチロでは\N親の目にかかわらず
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:17:01.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But in underground chinchiro, the players roll no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:01.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,子は必ず振る
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:08.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よっしゃ\Nしかし親の目が１であれば
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:06.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:10.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If the dealer rolls a 1, they're likely to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:10.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大抵の場合は勝てる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:17.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Seven players sit between Miyoshi and Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:16.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 三好は\Nカイジに回るまでの７人のうち
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:20.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目の出なかった大槻以外に全敗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:20.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Miyoshi loses to each of them except for Ohtsuki's roll of no dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:24.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とはいえ ここまでは\N皆 張りが小さい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:23.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But everyone else's bet has been low.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:29.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題は3000を張ったカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:28.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His worry is Kaiji, who bet 3,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:33.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このカイジに勝ちさえすれば\Nここまでの負けは帳消し
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:34.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If he beats Kaiji, he'll win back his losses, and more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:35.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,釣りが出る
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:38.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪いな 三好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:37.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:41.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰かが泣かなきゃならないのが\Nギャンブル
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:41.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In gambling, someone must always lose.{lit. "gin gambling someone must always cry"-try to work more of that in?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:46.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここはお前が泣く番だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And this is your turn to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:48.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji rolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:50.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ １投目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:53.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目は出ず
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:51.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No dice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:55.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, you're going to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:57.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,泣いてもらうぜ 三好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:57.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:03.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？\Nまたも目なし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:03.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No dice again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:11.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… バカな　よりによって\Nここで目が出ないなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:11.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Impossible... No dice again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:14.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No way! You're shitting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:16.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるわけねえ　ふざけるな\Nあるわけねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:16.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No fucking way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:19.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 運命の３投目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:18.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji makes his fateful third roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:25.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が負けるわけがねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:25.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:28.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けるはずがないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:27.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:36.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やるな カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:36.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wow, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:40.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここでこの目は なかなか出せんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:40.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That almost never comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:42.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's third roll...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:45.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ ３投目\Nあろうことかヒフミ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:44.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Is, of all things, 1-2-3!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:47.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,倍払い\Nウッソー！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:47.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He pays double!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:49.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:49.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:52.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大張りで最悪の目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:51.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The worst roll possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:55.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A tremendous reversal of fate, possible only in underground chinchiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:55.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この地下チンチロゆえに起きた\N大逆転
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:58.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 6000の払い
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:58.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji pays out 6,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:04.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうも　じゃ失礼して
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:04.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I may...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:08.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悔しい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:07.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I hate it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:10.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悔しい！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:10.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He hates it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:15.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悔しい\N悔しい！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:12.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I hate it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:13.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He hates it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I hate it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:16.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He hates it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが これでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:18.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But it's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:24.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これだ　これでこそ博打\Nギャンブルなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:19.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:22.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:24.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is gambling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:32.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,忘れてた この感覚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:32.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten this feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:36.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この悔しさ 憤り 血の逆流
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:33.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This bitterness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:36.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This rage, this chill in my veins!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:39.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ次だ　張った 張った
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:38.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay, next round! Place your bets!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:42.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:40.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:47.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:50.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ！飛び込め！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:49.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dive in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:53.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛び込んで いっそ翻弄されろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:53.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dive in! Even the crashing of the waves is an improvement!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:07.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 覚醒！張り続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji awakens!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:07.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He will continue betting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:11.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝っても負けても張りは3000
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:10.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Win or lose, he will bet 3,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:13.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,3000…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:12.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Three thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:15.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Three thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:15.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,3000！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:21.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{ed}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:38.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Gambling is... {15:25-}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:42.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dirtier than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:45.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:49.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It doesn't work without a twinge of pain! {-15:33}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.87,0:21:00.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tobaku Hakairoku Kaiji{\i0}: Chinchiro in Hades vol. 1,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:05.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,from the Underground Slave Labor arc, is now on sale.
